name: Dragon Ball Z - Shin Saiyajin Zetsumetsu Keikaku Chikyu Hen
summary: Dragon Ball Z Gaiden: Shin Saiyajin Zetsumetsu Keikaku - Chikyū-Hen is a video game released only in Japan on September 23, 1994. It is the first part of the Dragon Ball Z Gaiden: Zetsumetsu Keikaku series released on Playdia.
